  "instruction": "Create a small profile card page in VS Code at /home/user/Desktop/profile_card_grid. Create index.html and styles.css. The page should show the title \"Team Members\" and exactly three profile cards inside a container with id=\"card-grid\". Each profile card must use class=\"card\" and include three elements with classes name, role, and bio. Use simple CSS in styles.css so the cards are visually separated. Include CSS rules for body, #card-grid, and .card. Save both files.",
